long_description: Built in Keen's hometown of Portland, Ore., the casual Barika Slip-On shoes combine flattering details with construction that limits the use of harsh adhesives. Nubuck leather uppers have laser-cut floral designs and top stitching; lined with leather for great comfort. Patented rubber Toe Guards protect feet from scuffs, bumps and uneven sidewalks. Removable metatomical EVA footbeds support feet and cushion each step. Polyurethane outsoles are directly attached to the Keen Barika Slip-On shoes and do not use any adhesives.
